Payment will be charged to your account. Subscription auto-renews unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
pendingTranslations.By downloading, installing, or using Cen: By downloading, installing, or using Central Orbit, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, do not use the app.
pendingTranslations.Central Orbit is provided \"as is\" with: Central Orbit is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the service.
pendingTranslations.We may terminate or suspend your account: We may terminate or suspend your account at any time for violation of these terms. Upon termination, your right to use the service ceases immediately. You may delete your account at any time.
pendingTranslations.Central Orbit may embed third-party web: Central Orbit may embed third-party web content within tool tiles. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external websites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies.
pendingTranslations.We reserve the right to modify these ter: We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. We will notify users of material changes via email or in-app notification. Continued use of the service after changes constitutes acceptance.
pendingTranslations.Central Orbit is a workspace management: Central Orbit is a workspace management application that allows users to organize web-based tools and services into customizable workspaces. The app provides both free and premium (Pro) subscription tiers.
pendingTranslations.Central Orbit allows you to save URLs to: Central Orbit allows you to save URLs to third-party websites. We do not control, endorse, or assume responsibility for the content of any third-party website. You access third-party content at your own risk.
pendingTranslations.Payment will be charged to your Google P: Payment will be charged to your Google Play account. Subscription automatically renews unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Manage subscriptions in Google Play > Subscriptions.
pendingTranslations.Payment will be charged to your Apple ID: Payment will be charged to your Apple ID account. Subscription automatically renews unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Manage subscriptions in Settings > Apple ID > Subscriptions.
pendingTranslations.Your data is stored securely using indus: Your data is stored securely using industry-standard encryption. We use Convex as our database provider, which employs encryption at rest and in transit. We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.
pendingTranslations.Central Orbit is not intended for childr: Central Orbit is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we discover that a child under 13 has provided us with personal information, we will delete it immediately.
pendingTranslations.Your data is retained as long as your ac: Your data is retained as long as your account is active. You may request deletion of your account and all associated data at any time by contacting us. Upon deletion, all your workspaces, tools, and personal information will be permanently removed within 30 days.
